description:
This SEO course for Intermediates will help you get a better understanding of how SEO elements come together and how they should be prioritized when optimizing a website.

The course is structured into four major chapters:

1. Action plans: SEO and link building action plans

2. SEO in the Online Marketing and Management plan

3. Dig into Google Analytics like great SEOs do

4. What does and does not constitute SEO

The course also contains Resources which will help you put into practice the things you learn, either you will optimize your own website or you'll be offering SEO services.

Take this course now!
title: SEO Course for Intermediates
instructors: Company ONLINE REZISTANCE, Ela Iliesi, Simion Alexandru
